<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 18:07:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>呼吁释放加沙人质的集会席卷以色列各地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/rallies-calling-for-the-release-of-the-hostages-held-in-gaza-sweeping-across-israel/0000018b-9b32-d27d-a9fb-dbbbb0640000</link><description>一些家庭成员一直睡在特拉维夫国防总部前的帐篷里，并表示他们打算一直睡到人质获释为止。人质亲属称“我责怪内塔尼亚胡”</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 17:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/rallies-calling-for-the-release-of-the-hostages-held-in-gaza-sweeping-across-israel/0000018b-9b32-d27d-a9fb-dbbbb0640000</guid></item><item><title>纳斯鲁拉表示，他不会为了加沙而牺牲黎巴嫩，让哈马斯自生自灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/nasrallah-says-he-wont-sacrifice-lebanon-for-gaza-leaving-hamas-to-fend-for-itself/0000018b-9ad9-db71-a7df-ffdd53e10000</link><description>尽管地区盟友抱有期望，但真主党领导人明确表示，除非以色列深入黎巴嫩境内发动袭击或严重伤害平民，否则他不会发动全面战争</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 16:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/nasrallah-says-he-wont-sacrifice-lebanon-for-gaza-leaving-hamas-to-fend-for-itself/0000018b-9ad9-db71-a7df-ffdd53e10000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其召回驻以色列大使进行磋商；埃尔多安“抹掉”内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/turkey-recalls-ambassador-to-israel-for-consultations-erdogan-erases-netanyahu/0000018b-9ad4-d27d-a9fb-dafd2f710000</link><description>土耳其总统埃尔多安还表示，以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡不能再被视为土耳其的对手：“我们已经消灭了他”</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 15:48:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/turkey-recalls-ambassador-to-israel-for-consultations-erdogan-erases-netanyahu/0000018b-9ad4-d27d-a9fb-dafd2f710000</guid></item><item><title>当我们躲在安全室时，这些英雄出去拯救我们的基布兹——却再也没有回来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-we-hid-in-our-safe-room-these-heroes-went-out-to-save-our-kibbutz-and-never-returned/0000018b-9186-d7a8-afcf-bba7a2e30000</link><description>一名基布兹安全协调员在一名男孩被枪杀前救了他；一名边防警察士兵在他周围发现了五具恐怖分子的尸体；三名突击队员有时间一起拍了最后一张照片；两名巡逻士兵活着离开基布兹，但仍活着。上周在加沙陷落。纳哈奥兹英雄的生与死</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 14:30:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-we-hid-in-our-safe-room-these-heroes-went-out-to-save-our-kibbutz-and-never-returned/0000018b-9186-d7a8-afcf-bba7a2e30000</guid></item><item><title>美国官员称，哈马斯试图将其武装人员带着伤员和外国人偷偷带出加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-hamas-tried-to-sneak-out-fighters-with-wounded-and-foreign-nationals/0000018b-9a03-db71-a7df-ffcf50a00000</link><description>美国和埃及官员发现，被选中通过拉法过境点离开加沙进入埃及的人中，有三分之一是哈马斯战士，但最终撤离的 76 名受伤巴勒斯坦人中没有一人。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 11:25:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-hamas-tried-to-sneak-out-fighters-with-wounded-and-foreign-nationals/0000018b-9a03-db71-a7df-ffcf50a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列拦截从加沙发射的最远火箭；布林肯：哈马斯控制的加沙现状不能继续下去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-live/u-s-official-hamas-tried-to-sneak-fighters-out-of-gaza-rockets-fired-at-central-israel/0000018b-9859-dbad-abfb-d9dda8850000</link><description>加沙边境社区火箭警报响起 ■ 以色列国防军称部队正在加沙地带北部和南部行动 ■ 土耳其埃尔多安称他已经“消灭”了内塔尼亚胡 ■ 24 名以色列士兵和军官在加沙地面进攻中丧生 ■ 第三次访问以色列后，布林肯访问以色列约旦并将继续前往土耳其 ■ 242 名人质在加沙被扣押，40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称加沙有 9,000 多人丧生</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 05:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-live/u-s-official-hamas-tried-to-sneak-fighters-out-of-gaza-rockets-fired-at-central-israel/0000018b-9859-dbad-abfb-d9dda8850000</guid></item><item><title>在美国的支持下，以色列和乌克兰讨论泽伦斯基访问的可能性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-backing-israel-and-ukraine-discuss-possible-zelenskyy-visit/0000018b-9889-db71-a7df-fdcdae4b0000</link><description>讨论之际，拜登政府寻求建立亲美民主国家的统一战线，对抗俄罗斯-伊朗轴心</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 04:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article/.premium/with-u-s-backing-israel-and-ukraine-discuss-possible-zelenskyy-visit/0000018b-9889-db71-a7df-fdcdae4b0000</guid></item><item><title>记者询问以色列警察为何袭击他。 “因为你说阿拉伯语，”他们回答道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-reporter-asked-why-israeli-cops-attacked-him-because-you-spoke-arabic-they-replied/0000018b-9774-d8a6-a38b-dff70b0f0000</link><description>安全官员一直在骚扰代表当地和外国媒体报道战争的以色列阿拉伯公民记者</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 00:20:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-reporter-asked-why-israeli-cops-attacked-him-because-you-spoke-arabic-they-replied/0000018b-9774-d8a6-a38b-dff70b0f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡应该为 10 月 7 日的失败负责吗？这些利库德集团选民宁愿相信阴谋论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bibis-to-blame-for-oct-7-failures-likud-voters-prefer-to-believe-conspiracy-theories/0000018b-90c2-d477-a1ff-f7c2b8d10000</link><description>利库德集团在民调中的支持率大幅下滑，广大公众对政府感到愤怒。但对该党的一些传统据点的（有点危险的）访问揭示了为什么有些人仍然支持内塔尼亚胡——即使是现在</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 23:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bibis-to-blame-for-oct-7-failures-likud-voters-prefer-to-believe-conspiracy-theories/0000018b-90c2-d477-a1ff-f7c2b8d10000</guid></item><item><title>大卫·彼得雷乌斯将军向以色列发出警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/gen-david-petraeus-has-a-warning-for-israel/0000018b-96c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb0e090000</link><description>在这些战争期间指挥美国陆军的戴维·彼得雷乌斯将军表示，当以色列陷入加沙“异常艰难”的战场时，以色列军队必须从美国打击基地组织和伊斯兰国的痛苦经历中吸取教训</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 20:59:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/gen-david-petraeus-has-a-warning-for-israel/0000018b-96c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb0e090000</guid></item><item><title>作为大屠杀幸存者，我对以色列联合国特使的耻辱感到悲痛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-a-holocaust-survivor-im-saddened-by-the-israeli-un-envoys-disgrace/0000018b-9655-db71-a7df-ffdde0c20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 20:06:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-a-holocaust-survivor-im-saddened-by-the-israeli-un-envoys-disgrace/0000018b-9655-db71-a7df-ffdde0c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列驱逐了自战争开始以来滞留在约旦河西岸的数千名加沙工人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-deports-thousands-of-gazan-workers-stuck-in-west-bank-since-start-of-war/0000018b-95fd-db7e-af9b-ffff3d2f0000</link><description>战争爆发时，国家取消了滞留在以色列的劳工的工作许可证。在安全内阁决定驱逐他们并阻止加沙工人未来进入以色列后，将这些工人送回加沙成为可能</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 16:48:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-deports-thousands-of-gazan-workers-stuck-in-west-bank-since-start-of-war/0000018b-95fd-db7e-af9b-ffff3d2f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列加沙战争需要暂停以防止宗教战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-gaza-war-needs-a-humanitarian-pause-to-prevent-a-religious-war/0000018b-9596-db7e-af9b-ffd767a90000</link><description>埃及和沙特阿拉伯告诉华盛顿，加沙危机可能会复活极端组织，而人道主义暂停可能会维护对哈马斯战争的合法性</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 16:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israels-gaza-war-needs-a-humanitarian-pause-to-prevent-a-religious-war/0000018b-9596-db7e-af9b-ffd767a90000</guid></item><item><title>在反犹太主义抬头之际，以色列呼吁海外公民淡化“犹太人或以色列身份”的公开标志</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-03/ty-article/as-antisemitism-rises-israel-tells-citizens-abroad-to-downplay-jewish-or-israeli-identity/0000018b-95c4-d8a6-a38b-dfd7bc6c0000</link><description>以色列外交部建议公民推迟前往有旅行警告的国家；要求避免外化以色列和犹太符号，找出紧急服务的电话号码，并远离示威活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 15:49:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-03/ty-article/as-antisemitism-rises-israel-tells-citizens-abroad-to-downplay-jewish-or-israeli-identity/0000018b-95c4-d8a6-a38b-dfd7bc6c0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党纳斯鲁拉赞扬哈马斯 10 月 7 日的“英勇”袭击，称这是“100% 巴勒斯坦人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/hezbollahs-nasrallah-praises-heroic-oct-7-hamas-attack-says-it-was-100-palestinian/0000018b-95a4-db71-a7df-fded25b30000</link><description>真主党领导人赞扬哈马斯的袭击如何导致以色列发生“地震”，并警告说“那些想要防止地区战争的人必须迅速停止对加沙的侵略”</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 15:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/hezbollahs-nasrallah-praises-heroic-oct-7-hamas-attack-says-it-was-100-palestinian/0000018b-95a4-db71-a7df-fded25b30000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯在以色列访问期间敦促内塔尼亚胡在加沙“暂停人道主义行动”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/blinken-pushes-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pauses-in-gaza-during-israel-visit/0000018b-959f-db7e-af9b-ffdfa23a0000</link><description>这是美国国务卿自战争开始以来第三次访问以色列，他在会见内塔尼亚胡后表示，需要采取更多行动来“保护巴勒斯坦平民”。布林肯还指出，“屠杀的残酷性在许多人的记忆中很快就消失了”</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 15:40:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/blinken-pushes-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pauses-in-gaza-during-israel-visit/0000018b-959f-db7e-af9b-ffdfa23a0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙援助组织正在努力估计破坏程度。他们说情况从未如此糟糕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-aid-groups-struggle-to-estimate-extent-of-destruction-they-say-its-never-been-worse/0000018b-953e-d7a8-afcf-bfbf5b350000</link><description>在前几轮战争中，加沙地带的组织设法记录了损失，但现在他们甚至很难与员工保持联系。当以色列质疑加沙地带报告的伤亡人数时，组织表示数据可靠</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 15:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/gaza-aid-groups-struggle-to-estimate-extent-of-destruction-they-say-its-never-been-worse/0000018b-953e-d7a8-afcf-bfbf5b350000</guid></item><item><title>“我再也不会好起来了”：以色列的新移民如何应对战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-never-going-to-be-okay-again-how-new-immigrants-to-israel-are-coping-with-the-war/0000018b-8fa0-d477-a1ff-ffa057ef0000</link><description>《国土报》采访了近年来移居以色列的六名移民，以了解他们在战时的新家园最让他们惊讶的是什么。尽管如此，没有人后悔选择搬到这里</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 14:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/im-never-going-to-be-okay-again-how-new-immigrants-to-israel-are-coping-with-the-war/0000018b-8fa0-d477-a1ff-ffa057ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可能为参与10月7日大屠杀的哈马斯恐怖分子设立特别法庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-may-establish-special-court-for-hamas-terrorists-who-took-part-in-massacres/0000018b-94c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb00bd0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，以色列在加沙边境附近的社区关押了数百名涉嫌参与哈马斯屠杀的人，并一直在系统地收集战争罪和反人类罪的数字证据</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 12:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-may-establish-special-court-for-hamas-terrorists-who-took-part-in-massacres/0000018b-94c9-db7e-af9b-ffcb00bd0000</guid></item><item><title>看到南部的恐怖，以色列北部的居民感到他们必须自力更生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/seeing-the-horrors-in-the-south-galilee-residents-feel-they-must-fend-for-themselves/0000018b-9469-db7e-af9b-ffebd7ad0000</link><description>私人拖拉机挖的战壕、临时搭建的射击阵地以及自愿担任观察员的平民：西加利利和上加利利的居民不再相信国家会保护他们。一位居民说，“感觉我们又回到了建州前的日子”</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 11:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/seeing-the-horrors-in-the-south-galilee-residents-feel-they-must-fend-for-themselves/0000018b-9469-db7e-af9b-ffebd7ad0000</guid></item></channel></rss>